    '-lowlight-color[de-emphasize pixel differences with this color]:color:' \
    '-metric[difference metric]:type:(AE DSSIM FUZZ MAE MEPP MSE NCC PAE PHASH PSNR RMSE SSIM)' \
    '-monitor[monitor progress]' \
